data.description: Discover the allure of this inviting 3-bedroom Cape Cod home that seamlessly blends classic charm with modern comforts. Inside, you'll find a spacious living area bathed in natural light, complemented by a recently updated kitchen featuring brand new stainless steel appliances and a cozy dining area. Three bedrooms offer ample storage. Second floor is a primary bedroom oasis with a large bedroom, walk in closet, and full bath suite. The partially finished basement expands your living space, and a covered patio in the back yard beckons you outdoors for relaxation with a beautiful koi pond. A one-car detached garage. Your dream home awaits – don't miss the chance to make it yours! Schedule a viewing today. Home warranty included!
